    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the festive fries have been cooking for 10-15 min, add your<strong> meat-free patties</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray and put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until the patties have started to brown</p><p>Once the patties have started to brown, top half of the patties<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>with your <strong>cheese flavour slices</strong> and return the tray to the oven for 2-3 min or until the cheese has melted</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1604315123912-x200.jpg",
