            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the burgers are in the oven, cut the ends off your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> and slice in half</p><p>Tip: Don’t chuck the crusts away. Instead, turn them into croutons!</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>,<strong> </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper and shred</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1604315142510-x200.jpg",
