        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced ciabatta</strong>,<strong> </strong>cut-side down, and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted</p><p>Once done, add the <strong>sliced brioche buns</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted</p><p>Tip: You'll need to do this in batches!</p>",
      "order": 6,
