      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything is almost done, add the <strong>toasted ciabatta</strong> to the <strong>gravy</strong> and set aside for 1-2 min or until it's started to soak up the gravy</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
